<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f5f5;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
        }

        .container {
            width: 80%;
            margin: 50px auto;
            padding: 20px;
            background-color: #fff;
            border-radius: 4px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .content {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 32px;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
            color: #4a86e8;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 18px;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        .activation-code {
            display: inline-block;
            background-color: #4a86e8;
            color: #fff;
            padding: 15px 30px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            font-size: 24px;
            font-weight: bold;
            text-decoration: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }

        .activation-code:hover {
            background-color: #356de8;
        }

        .otp-image {
            display: inline-block;
            width: 50px;
            height: 50px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background-color: #4a86e8;
            margin-left: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
            animation: rotate 3s linear infinite;
        }

        @keyframes rotate {
            0% {
                transform: rotate(0deg);
            }
            100% {
                transform: rotate(360deg);
            }
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            margin-top: 50px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #4a86e8;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="content">
            <h1>Welcome to Digital Learning!</h1>
            <p>Hello <%= user.name %>,</p>
            <p>We are thrilled to welcome you to Digital Learning, your gateway to a world of knowledge and opportunities!</p>
            <p>To get started, please use the following activation code:</p>
            <a href="#" class="activation-code">
                <span class="activation-code-text"><%= activationCode %></span>
                <span class="otp-image"></span>
            </a>
            <p>This code is valid for the next 15 minutes.</p>
            <p>If you need any assistance, please don't hesitate to reach out to our support team at <a href="mailto:example@gmail.com">example@gmail.com</a>.</p>
            <p>Happy learning!</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
